r nearly half a century. Even more influentially, it is the name of her daughter  Queen Elizabeth II  (  b. 1926 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elisabeth d'Antoing was born about 1145, in France as the daughter of Heer Hugo van Antoing en Epinoy and Flandrine van Namen. She married Heer Diederik II van Ligne in January 1150."},"et":{"about 1145–":"umbes 1145–Surnud","1145–Female":"1145–Surnud","1130–1190":"1130–1190","–1190":"–1190","1180–1246":"1180–1246","–Male":"Surnud","1095–Female":"1095–Surnud","1190":"1190","1246":"1246","about 1180":"umbes 1180","1145":"1145","about 1145":"umbes 1145","1130":"1130","januari 1150":"jaanuar 1150","1150":"1150","1095":"1095","1180":"1180","Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgium":"Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgia","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1145–":"noin 1145–Kuollut","1145–Female":"1145–Kuollut","1130–1190":"1130–1190","–1190":"–1190","1180–1246":"1180–1246","–Male":"Kuollut","1095–Female":"1095–Kuollut","1190":"1190","1246":"1246","about 1180":"noin 1180","1145":"1145","about 1145":"noin 1145","1130":"1130","januari 1150":"tammikuu 1150","1150":"1150","1095":"1095","1180":"1180","Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgium":"Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgia","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1145–":"environ 1145–Décédée","1145–Female":"1145–Décédée","1130–1190":"1130–1190","–1190":"–1190","1180–1246":"1180–1246","–Male":"Décédé","1095–Female":"1095–Décédée","1190":"1190","1246":"1246","about 1180":"environ 1180","1145":"1145","about 1145":"environ 1145","1130":"1130","januari 1150":"janvier 1150","1150":"1150","1095":"1095","1180":"1180","Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgium":"Ligne, Ath, Hainaut, Belgique","France":"France","lifeSummary":"Elisabeth d'Antoing est née environ 1145, à France, fille de Heer Hugo van Antoing en Epinoy et Flandrine van Namen. Elle a épousé Heer Diederik II van Ligne en janvier 1150."},"de":{"about 1145–":"um 1145–Verstorben","1145–Female":"1145–Verstorben","1130–1190":"1130–1190","–1190":"–1190","1180–1246":"1180–1246","–Male":"Verstorben",